# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# USS Academy — Cloudflare Pages _redirects
#
# Order matters: Cloudflare evaluates top to bottom and returns on first
# match. Specific rules MUST come above the catch-all splat at the end.
# Cloudflare Pages also only falls through to _redirects when no static
# file or asset matches — so legitimate .html pages are never hijacked.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Existing 200 rewrites (keep clean URL at user-facing path) ──
/tos                        /terms.html                            200
/class-registration         /waiver-class-registration.html        200
/exam-registration          /waiver-exam-registration.html         200
/range-waiver               /waiver-range.html                     200

# ── Existing 301 canonicals ──
/privacy-policy             /privacy.html                          301
/terms-of-service           /terms.html                            301
/our-services               /                                      301

# ── Legacy Wix / old-site URL recovery (Apr 2026 — GSC showed 24 404s dating to 2022) ──
